ontext":"In &quot;Wisdom \u0627\u0644\u062d\u0643\u0645\u0629&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Wisdom \u0627\u0644\u062d\u0643\u0645\u0629","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/wisdom-al-hikmah\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":42060,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2024\/07\/24\/angels-front-rows\/","url_meta":{"origin":31787,"position":1},"title":"Hadith on Salat: Angels bless the front prayer rows","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"July 24, 2024","format":false,"excerpt":"Al-Bara\u2019 ibn \u2018Azib reported: The Messenger of Allah, peace and blessings be upon him, used to pass through the prayer rows from one side to the other, setting their chests and shoulders in order. The Prophet would say, \u201cLet not your hearts conflict,\u201d and the Prophet would say, \u201cVerily, Allah\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Righteousness \u0627\u0644\u0628\u0631&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Righteousness \u0627\u0644\u0628\u0631","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/righteousness-al-birr\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":20126,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2015\/01\/03\/dhikr-allah-boasts-angels\/","url_meta":{"origin":31787,"position":2},"title":"Hadith on Dhikr: Allah boasts to angels of those who remember Him","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"January 3, 2015","format":false,"excerpt":"Mu\u2019awiyah reported: The Messenger of Allah, peace and blessings be upon him, came out to a gathering of his companions and he said, \u201cWhy are you sitting?\u201d They said, \u201cWe are sitting to remember Allah and to praise him for guiding us to Islam and blessing us with it.\u201d The\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Faith \u0627\u0644\u0627\u064a\u0645\u0627\u0646&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Faith \u0627\u0644\u0627\u064a\u0645\u0627\u0646","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/faith-iman\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":25293,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2017\/10\/22\/when-the-prophet-forgot-ablution\/","url_meta":{"origin":31787,"position":3},"title":"Hadith on Prayer: When the Prophet forgot ablution for prayer","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"October 22, 2017","format":false,"excerpt":"Abu Huraira reported: The prayer had been prepared and the rows straightened, then the Messenger of Allah, peace and blessings be upon him, came out to us. When he stood in his place of prayer, he remembered that he was in a state of ritual impurity (junub). The Prophet said\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Wisdom \u0627\u0644\u062d\u0643\u0645\u0629&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Wisdom \u0627\u0644\u062d\u0643\u0645\u0629","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/wisdom-al-hikmah\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":31714,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2019\/06\/02\/dua-hamd-kathir-tayyib-mubarak\/","url_meta":{"origin":31787,"position":4},"title":"Hadith on Dua: Praise to Allah, abundant, good, blessed therein","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"June 2, 2019","format":false,"excerpt":"Anas reported: A man came and entered the row of prayer, breathing heavily. The man said, \u201cAll praise is due to Allah, abundant praise, goodness, and blessings therein.\u201d When the Messenger of Allah, peace and blessings be upon him, finished the prayer, he said, \u201cWhich one of you spoke these\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Faith \u0627\u0644\u0627\u064a\u0645\u0627\u0646&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Faith \u0627\u0644\u0627\u064a\u0645\u0627\u0646","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/faith-iman\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":17068,"url":"https:\/\/ww